                                "byte_start": 76800,
                                "byte_stop": 91220,
                                "text": "Thank you, Mr. Justice Rehnquist."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 3.588,
                                "stop": 10.228,
                                "byte_start": 91220,
                                "byte_stop": 117760,
                                "text": "Justice Powell will announce the disposition of Alexander against Gardner-Denver Company."
